{"tid":1814640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「暖氣小隊」宣佈正式退場","createTime":"2020-01-07T03:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:16:35.000Z","uid":320676,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9aebf69a0f145f0e1004ef1f30913b6def672b","tid":1814640,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"知唔知道勇武退場手足想你哋做咩?想你哋都做勇武啊暖氣撚！<br />\n<br />\n立即停止內鬥，落街去買gear，準備長期同港共、支共嘅戰爭。無刀嘅買定把，無豬嘴買豬嘴，無泳鏡買泳鏡，學下整火魔，買定枝通渠水，鎚仔，一字批。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係要有戰鬥嘅心態，狗係你嘅仇敵，你唔殺狗，狗就殺你<br />\n<br />\n我而家宣布「暖氣小隊」正式退出被竇，落街真正打狗救人，連登有幾十萬人用，點解唔去做實事，而係喺連登玩分化？<br />\n<br />\n要對得起死去嘅手足得一個方法，就係達成佢哋嘅願望「全民勇武，推翻港共」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">千祈唔好做犯法嘅嘢</span>"},{"pid":"5f99363f3ba7c6de8fa053718cae7214659c8dc1","tid":1814640,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"你老母<br />\n搞港獨就靜靜地<br />\n贏又靜靜地<br />\n<br />\nQuit game 就大大聲？"},{"pid":"e12f6ecc40d0c564e8e11fa75279789458e03e39","tid":1814640,"uid":195120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"退場床鋪 進場抗爭"},{"pid":"79ca48005a0c7dca9febf8a7e9a088a02c19decb","tid":1814640,"uid":195120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f99363f3ba7c6de8fa053718cae7214659c8dc1","tid":1814640,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"你老母<br />\n搞港獨就靜靜地<br />\n贏又靜靜地<br />\n<br />\nQuit game 就大大聲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"Ching 你係咪睇錯d野"},{"pid":"4a5e4e3eb024882e11552e78b1ed178922b7211a","tid":1814640,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79ca48005a0c7dca9febf8a7e9a088a02c19decb","tid":1814640,"uid":195120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f99363f3ba7c6de8fa053718cae7214659c8dc1","tid":1814640,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"你老母<br />\n搞港獨就靜靜地<br />\n贏又靜靜地<br />\n<br />\n